title: Updated Spectacular corner home.
posting_body: ['Updated Spectacular corner home.', 'Two bedrooms, one bath, on a large 13,000 SF lot.', "The 106' frontage on Sheridan ST provides excellent exposure to use the house as a home or office, or maybe both, since the zoning is (RO) and can be used for office, Professional or Residential.", 'New fresh paint, updated kitchen, new appliances, and updated bathroom.', 'The property has three sheds with electricity; one is used as a laundry room, and the other two as storage.', 'The property is located one block off Federal Hwy and a few minutes from Dania Beach Pier.', "Don't miss this gem.", '1518 SW 2nd', 'Ave # 0 DANIA BEACH, FL 33004-4209', 'PROPERTY ID:  GTA11223715', 'Type of Property: SINGLE', 'List Price:\t$2,600', 'Bedrooms:  2', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'SqFt (Liv):¤927', 'CALL OR TEXT TODAY', 'show contact info', 'Global Trust Realty, LLC posts properties for a 30 day period of time.', ' Due to current high rental demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', ' All prices are subject to change based upon availability.', 'All information is deemed to be correct but not guaranteed.', 'Listed and Brokered by:Luxe Properties']
